bhagacetaseti bhagopabhogāśaktiṃ kṛtvā bhagavato ’kṣobhyasya śiromārgeṇa mahāsukhena dravībhūyād avadhūtīnāḍīm adhiṣṭhāyākṣobhyaśukreṇa saha patet | vajrarandhreṇa devīpadme | tataḥ padmasuśireṇa dakṣiṇakukṣim adhiṣṭhāya hūṃkārarūpeṇa | bījaṃ dhyātvā tatpariṇatācalarūpeṇa devīpadmamārgeṇa niḥsṛtya tayor agrataḥ tiṣṭhed iti samudāyārthaḥ ||
